request.description:
Method: POST
URL: {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/jobs/cancel
Auth: Admin access token with jobs:cancel permission
Body: target_type vehicle|market|stall, target_ref, optional worker_action and reason. For vehicle, worker_action defaults to requeue and returns cancelled workers to the front of the queue in assignment accept order. Use open_app only when admin does not want to return workers to queue. For market/stall, omit worker_action or send none.
Examples:
Vehicle requeue: { "target_type": "vehicle", "target_ref": "{{ticketNo}}" }
Vehicle open_app: { "target_type": "vehicle", "target_ref": "{{ticketNo}}", "worker_action": "open_app" }
Market: { "target_type": "market", "target_ref": "{{marketCode}}" }
Stall: { "target_type": "stall", "target_ref": "{{boothCode}}" }

